. Riding in the boat does tend to blow out the pilot light in the device but a few clicks of the starter and it&#8217;s going again. They have models specifically for hunters (no game alarming scent) and lanterns for your back yard.</p><p>-- Jim Mays</p><p>Thermacell Mosquito Repellent Appliance<br />
