 cash/note pockets, so there’s plenty of room to carry more than enough.</p><p>So here’s my short review. The Yasutomo 2020 Wa-Ben wallet is fabulous piece of gear, and I recommend it highly for anyone looking to lighten their everyday carry load.</p><p>-- <a href=\"http://fordsbasement.com/\">Tom Fassbender</a></p><p>Yasutomo 2020 Wa-Ben Wallet<br />
